Purpose
-------
This project is a private academic/university collaboration ("Códigos Primordiais").
This license is intended to allow classmates/collaborators to contribute while
keeping the project private.

Permissions (for approved collaborators)
---------------------------------------
If you are an approved collaborator of this repository for academic purposes,
you may:

- View, clone, and run the project for academic evaluation.
- Modify the project and commit/push changes to this repository.
- Share the project and its modifications ONLY with other approved collaborators
  of this same academic project.

Restrictions
------------
You may NOT:

- Publish the repository or its contents publicly (including public forks).
- Redistribute the project outside the approved collaborator group.
- Use this project (code, assets, story, designs) in other projects.
- Use this project for commercial purposes.

Third-party content
-------------------
Some assets may be subject to third-party licenses. When adding third-party
content, include the license text under the `licences/` directory and follow
its terms.

No warranty
-----------
The project is provided "as is", without warranty of any kind.

Contact
-------
For permissions beyond this license (e.g., public release, portfolio use),
contact the repository owner/maintainer.
